Sinesis and Sinister walked up and did a salute.

"Our orders?" Sinesis asked.

"yes, send us out!" Sinister said. Sinister looked over at Blizzard, he
stares at her with his heart beating fast. Sinesis nudged him.

"She's beautiful." Sinister said. He walked over to Blizzard.

"Hi, I'm Sinister, what kind of threat...Sorry, I meant to say, what is your
name?" Sinister asked Blizzard...
